rating_comment: The place is good, needs little fixing on door nobs, all three bedrooms has very little balcony it should be little more bigger. The apartment from the neighboring building next to master bedroom is very loud up-to 4 in the morning I think some college students messing there. The owner Mr.Mir Is very responsive and helpful.
